<h4><a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-020-02717-3">史上第一张黑洞照片被做成了视频</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1368490" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/blackhole.gif" alt="" width="800" height="776" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/blackhole.gif 800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/blackhole-360x349.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/blackhole-768x745.gif 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<p>《自然》消息，事件视界望远镜（EHT）将去年史上第一张黑洞照片制成了视频。他们挖掘了黑洞相关的旧数据，并结合去年的黑洞照片和数学模型，以呈现出黑洞在过去八年里发生的改变。</p>
<p>虽然这个模型仍存在推测成分，但它也可为天文学家提供关于黑洞的洞见。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.theverge.com/2020/9/24/21453709/ring-always-home-cam-indoor-drone-security-camera-price-specs-features-amazon?scrolla=5eb6d68b7fedc32c19ef33b4">Ring 最新的监控摄像能化身无人机，飞到用户想看的房间</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1368491" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/20200921_image_blog_flyingcamera_sidebyside_2910x1637_fcc_rgb.0.jpg" alt="" width="920" height="613" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/20200921_image_blog_flyingcamera_sidebyside_2910x1637_fcc_rgb.0.jpg 920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/20200921_image_blog_flyingcamera_sidebyside_2910x1637_fcc_rgb.0-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/20200921_image_blog_flyingcamera_sidebyside_2910x1637_fcc_rgb.0-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 920px) 100vw, 920px" /></p>
<p>The Verge 消息，Ring 推出家庭安全监控摄像 Always Home Cam 能化身无人机，飞到用户想看的不同房间中，随后，无人机将飞回到底座上进行充电。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1368493" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ezgif.com-optimize.gif" alt="" width="400" height="220" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ezgif.com-optimize.gif 400w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ezgif.com-optimize-360x198.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /></p>
<p>这款监控预计将于明年出货，定价为 249.99 美元（约人民币 1728 元）。</p>
<h4>联想发布 ThinkBook 新青年创造本系列新品</h4>
